snippet.title: Naïca - Official Cinematic Trailer (Intro)
snippet.description:
Every adventure starts with a cry for help. Answer the call and begin your journey to save Naïca!

Join us: https://naicaonline.com

#Naïca #MMORPG

Naïca is an original 2D MMORPG designed in pixel art with a lot of customization. Naïca is available on Android, iOS, and PC in cross-play/cross-save.

Discord : https://discord.gg/naicaonline
Facebook : https://www.facebook.com/naicaonline/
Twitter : https://twitter.com/NaicaOnline/
Instagram : https://www.instagram.com/naicaonline/

All rights regarding the game are reserved by Millenium Studio.
All music rights reserved by Gabriel Palmieri: https://gabrielpalmieri.bandcamp.com/
Voice actress is Sarah Ruth Thomas: https://twitter.com/SarahRuthVoice
